{"tid":609513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"對付戲院講嘢嘅仆街","createTime":"2018-03-29T06:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T17:51:05.000Z","uid":124894,"like":246,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a41c814cd3ce8573caaaee23aecf4aabde58a3","tid":609513,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:13:53.000Z","msg":"尋晚電影節，後面條八婆嘈撚住晒，屌完佢仲fight back，話我啤佢，又話佢後面啲人都無出聲...<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚憎啲人睇戲講嘢，悶嘅就走，次撚次俾佢哋嘈完都無咩心機繼續睇。你講嘢話完你就收皮啦，仲要反擊！<br />\n<br />\n大家平時又點應對呢。"},{"pid":"1358c93a3d93fbd4de8f7acc2f8dfdbf393a607d","tid":609513,"uid":63505,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"表現到你有攪炒既決心，正路冇人想睇唔哂套戲"},{"pid":"f0be524cc90b3cac9c35800cb531a27769fc1e5d","tid":609513,"uid":28802,"like":65,"dislike":5,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"攞定個膠袋佢一嘈嘅你谷啲氣落個膠袋度再一嘢打爆佢 全院靜曬"},{"pid":"157dc72f80d54b0a5862bcf83636b298da6ae706","tid":609513,"uid":124894,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"quote":{"pid":"1358c93a3d93fbd4de8f7acc2f8dfdbf393a607d","tid":609513,"uid":63505,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"表現到你有攪炒既決心，正路冇人想睇唔哂套戲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"只要有多一個人附和，就即刻收佢皮"},{"pid":"7273fbf9b5d6d0ad09cc146694dccb6b11044417","tid":609513,"uid":17152,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"開頭會o殊佢，唔聽就大大聲屌佢，但有2次係屌完都唔收聲，我都唔知仲可以做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2559efc2a5f2f28f245c58d83f9636260680c2e1","tid":609513,"uid":51495,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"我試過<br />\n坐我後面既<br />\n起身，指撚住條八婆叫佢收聲"},{"pid":"30a57410696dac8a2ae18ad33c31be21531c7a2c","tid":609513,"uid":124894,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"大家遇