.g.陣間去邊度食飯)等，一律槍斃。電話亮芒超過十五秒者，罰款一萬。<br />\n13歲以下小朋友在觀看劇情片前需先作行為檢定測試，以確認不會在場問問題，嘈喧巴閉。<br />\n嚴禁弱智人士尤其係女人(弱智人士指低b 情侶：蠢撚到閪嘅女朋友，以為自己巧威威其實講廢話嘅男朋友)進入戲院，可能都要做智力測試<br />\n睇恐怖片講野壯膽嘅人需單獨囚禁，強逼24小時睇VR恐怖片，這是為你好的。<br />\n暫時初步係諗到咁。</blockquote><br />\n點樣可以分析到內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f19fb9058ae1f4897e48701ca987314df6efa96","tid":609513,"uid":38988,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n我女朋友唔叻<br />\n要我講解個劇情<br />\n我已經盡量細聲"},{"pid":"c2adc242022017c2164df6b9afef663286f88784","tid":609513,"uid":22898,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"6f19fb9058ae1f4897e48701ca987314df6efa96","tid":609513,"uid":38988,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n我女朋友唔叻<br />\n要我講解個劇情<br />\n我已經盡量細聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:04:56.000Z","msg":"我明，但係我都想講句：「下次唔好帶女朋友入場睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"08e435bde67269db956a489301be5de922a6c407","tid":609513,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c2adc242022017c2164df6b9afef663286f88784","tid":609513,"uid":22898,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"6f19fb9058ae1f4897e48701ca987314df6efa96","tid":609513,"uid":38988,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n我女朋友唔叻<br />\n要我講解個劇情<br />\n我已經盡量細聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:04:56.000Z","msg":"我明，但係我都想講句：「下次唔好帶女朋友入場睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"我其實有叫佢睇人劇透個啲片先入場<br />\n但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998dedc9454da6d65b9c1b52f52e1daafccf